items.name: Chat-with-PDF-using-Groq-LLM
items.description: This project is an interactive PDF-based chatbot that allows users to upload one or more PDF documents and ask questions based on their content. It uses Groq’s LLM (e.g., Gemma2-9b-It) for answering questions with detailed and context-aware responses, and sentence-transformer embeddings with ChromaDB for efficient semantic search.

items.name: CANES
items.description: Medical image segmentation remains a crucial challenge in automated cardiac diagnosis. We present the CANES-Net architecture, a novel architecture combining U-Net with Transformer attention, Mamba selective state-space modeling with class-specific loss functions to improve multi-class cardiac structure segmentation on the ACDC dataset.
